    margin:0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-weight:600;
  ">
    The Work in Environment
  </p>

  <h2 style="
    font-size:clamp(24px, 2.8vw, 30px);
    font-weight:600;
    color:#056367;
    margin:0 0 1.25rem 0;
  ">
    Wellbeing Beyond the Individual
  </h2>

  <h3 style="
    font-size:18px;
    font-weight:600;
    margin:0 0 1.25rem 0;
  ">
    Wellbeing Is Also About Where We Land
  </h3>

  <p>
    My work in preventive health and wellbeing also recognises something often overlooked:
    <strong>our environments matter</strong>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Alongside my consulting and coaching work, I manage a small portfolio of furnished rental homes, spaces designed to offer comfort, calm, and stability during periods of transition. Whether supporting professionals on temporary placements or individuals needing a fully furnished, ready-to-live-in environment, this work reflects the same principles I bring to wellbeing: safety, intentionality, and ease.
  </p>

  <p>
    While this is not a public-facing service, I believe in transparency and alignment. The way we live, rest, and recover is inseparable from our health, and I strive to ensure that every part of my work reflects that understanding.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
    <a href="https://www.marshakerrtalley.com/rentals"
       style="color:#319fa2;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">
      View rental information
    </a>
  </p>

</section>

      <div style="padding:14px 6px 6px; max-width:72ch;">

        <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.8vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          My work did not begin in theory.
          It was shaped through personal experience,
          where I came to understand how prolonged stress and emotional strain
          quietly reshape identity, confidence, and purpose.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.8vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          That understanding led me to focus on prevention rather than recovery alone.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.8vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          Alongside my consultancy and wellbeing work, I am the author of
          <strong style="color:#056367;">The Decision Is Just the Beginning</strong>
          and <strong style="color:#056367;">Healing from Emotional Traumas</strong>,
          exploring agency, emotional awareness, and sustainable personal change.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 22px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.8vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          I have spent over two decades in education, teaching and supporting people
          with diverse learning profiles and special educational needs,
          alongside curriculum development and educational leadership.
        </p>

        <!-- COACHING & CONSULTING -->
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:clamp(22px,4vw,24px);font-weight:900;color:#056367;">
          Coaching and Consulting
        </h3>

        <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.6vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          My work spans both coaching and consulting.
          These approaches overlap but serve different purposes,
          used intentionally depending on context and responsibility.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.6vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          <strong style="color:#056367;">Coaching</strong> focuses on the individual,
          creating space for reflection, sense-making, and personal authorship.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 22px;font-size:clamp(16px,3.6vw,18px);line-height:1.65;">
          <strong style="color:#056367;">Consulting</strong> focuses on systems,
          roles, and environments, supporting organisations to strengthen
          conditions that sustain wellbeing, capacity, and retention.
        </p>

        <!-- SCOPE -->
        <h4 style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:clamp(18px,3.8vw,20px);font-weight:900;color:#056367;">
          Clarifying the scope of this work
        </h4>

        <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:clamp(15px,3.4vw,17px);line-height:1.65;">
          This work is not therapy, counselling, or clinical intervention.
          It does not involve diagnosis or treatment of mental health conditions.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0;font-size:clamp(15px,3.4vw,17px);line-height:1.65;">
          Preventive wellbeing support focuses on awareness, steadiness,
          and practical strategies that sit alongside existing
          therapeutic or safeguarding support where needed.
        </p>

      </div>
    </details>

  </div>
